{"tid":2005832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制派楊永杰：點解政府唔搵車車返係富豪酒店檢疫完既人返機場","createTime":"2020-05-07T11:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T11:24:13.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eee802a455d32db4bc0c5a569b98435dfb74bef7","tid":2005832,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:13:29.000Z","msg":"政府上月先斬後奏，租用九龍城富豪東方酒店作入境人士等候檢疫結果的設施。九龍城區議會今日下午開會，食衞局副局長徐德義到區議會交代。建制派楊永杰在會上語出驚人，認為局方應安排車輛將完成等候檢測結果的人士，由富豪東方酒店送返機場，「可能佢住機場隔離呢。」徐德義聽到後一度感到惘然，民主派的李軒朗則不禁大笑。<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他詳情：<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073173&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=2726f6c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073173&h=b43293e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073173</a>"},{"pid":"478ae83d1b0212d4eed323617a1ed7f3d840fde6","tid":2005832,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"可以On99到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b13521be6ba5749d23cad8e26366164d3c76508","tid":2005832,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eee802a455d32db4bc0c5a569b98435dfb74bef7","tid":2005832,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:13:29.000Z","msg":"政府上月先斬後奏，租用九龍城富豪東方酒店作入境人士等候檢疫結果的設施。九龍城區議會今日下午開會，食衞局副局長徐德義到區議會交代。建制派楊永杰在會上語出驚人，認為局方應安排車輛將完成等候檢測結果的人士，由富豪東方酒店送返機場，「可能佢住機場隔離呢。」徐德義聽到後一度感到惘然，民主派的李軒朗則不禁大笑。<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他詳情：<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073173&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=2726f6c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073173&h=b43293e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node